bio.openEndedText: Rent N Go LLC started our business 7 years ago on Turo. We started with one car and expanded slowly on Turo. Our business is ran by two brothers Dijesh Mathew & Naveen Thomas who genuinely care about giving a product at it's best condition with a fair price to our guests. Our guests experience is our primary goal and hope we can assist with a rental process that’s above standards.

I am down to earth person, I enjoy meeting new people and making lasting friendship. I love cooking and  traveling. My services are efficient, affordable and  very hospitable. Be my guest💜💜

Thank you for your understanding and Please be my GUEST 😊

Hello, my esteemed travelers,

Allow me to introduce myself as a dedicated enthusiast of both travel and the art of hospitality. My profound love for automobiles and the sheer joy of driving my passion for providing an exceptional experience to fellow adventurers. 

My heart finds immense joy in connecting with individuals from diverse corners of the globe, as I believe it is through these interactions that we gain invaluable insights into different cultures and lifestyles. It's a pleasure to extend my warm welcome to you as a Turo host.

In my collection, you'll find a variety of vehicles spanning different price ranges, all eagerly awaiting the opportunity to accompany you on your upcoming journeys. I take pride in my commitment to accommodating reasonable requests and addressing any specific needs that renters may have. For those considering long-term rentals, please don't hesitate to reach out, as I offer exclusive discounts for extended stays.

Should you have any inquiries or require further information, please feel free to reach out via text at two eight one, eight seven six, seven eight two three.

As a bonus, if you're seeking a vacation house or a private room in Houston or any other destination worldwide, I invite you to explore my offerings on Airbnb: https://www.airbnb.com/users/109509081/listings.

Thank you for considering me as your host, and I look forward to making your travels as memorable and enjoyable as possible. Safe and happy travels!

My name is Lester and I'm excited to share my car with you through Turo. I've been a Turo host since 2021. I believe in providing my guests with a high-quality, reliable, and clean car that they can trust to get them where they need to go.

When you rent from me, you can expect great communication and flexibility. I'm happy to work with you to arrange pickup and drop-off times that are convenient for you. I'll also provide you with a thorough orientation of the car so you feel comfortable and confident behind the wheel.

Overall, I'm committed to providing an exceptional Turo experience. I'm confident that you'll enjoy renting from me and I look forward to making your trip a success!

My fiancé and I started this business as a way to help others. At the beginning of 2021 we dealt with a ton of car trouble which forced us into the car market. We quickly found that the outrageous prices made it difficult to not only purchase but also rent a vehicle. We struggled to find affordable transportation until we came across the Turo platform.  

Ms. Jones allowed us to rent her car which provided us with a reliable, clean, and affordable transportation to meet our professional and family needs until we were able to purchase a car. We want to provide the same resources and level of service that Ms. Jones extended to our family. We are a business but our WHY is so much deeper than revenue. We strive to provide people with affordable and reliable rental vehicles with top level service to meet their needs. We are here to serve and look forward to partnering with you. Peace & Blessings.
